fields.value: Replication Data for: Controls on the formation of lunar multiring basins

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This is the replication data for Controls on the formation of lunar multiring basins

ZIp files contain input and output for iSALE simulation. Matlab fig files are included other figures.

publicationCitation.value: Johnson, B. C., Andrews-Hanna, J. C., Collins, G. S., Freed, A. M., Melosh, H. J., & Zuber, M. T. (2018). Controls on the formation of lunar multiring basins. Journal of Geophysical Research: Planets, 123. https://doi.org/10.1029/ 2018JE005765
